text: The Renault 25 was a car made by Renault. It replaced the Renault 20 in 1983, and was replaced by the Renault Safrane in 1992. == Engines == * 2.0 76 kW (103 hp) * 2.0 i 88 kW (120 hp) * 2.0 i 12V 99 kW (135 hp) * 2.2 i 79 kW (107 hp) and 90 kW (122 hp) * 2.5 V6 Turbo 134 kW (182 hp) and 151 kW (205 hp) * 2.7 V6 106 kW (144 hp) * 2.9 V6 102 kW (139 hp), 112 kW (152 hp) and 118 kW (160 hp) * 2.1 Diesel 48 kW (65 hp) * 2.1 Turbodiesel 65 kW (88 hp) 25 Category:Front wheel drive vehicles Category:1980s automobiles Category:1990s automobiles
